# ACTIVE THREAD TRACKING

When frontend opens thread:

```ts
socket.emit('conversation.opened', {
  conversationId,
  participantId,
});
```

Server stores active view.

When thread closes:

```ts
socket.emit('conversation.closed', {
  conversationId,
});
```

Server removes active view.

